This directory tools for plotting information from transaction logs produced from taskvine applications:

vine_plot_tr.py - produces a plot depicting the tasks executing on each worker.

	Running the program: python vine_plot_tr.py <transaction_log> <title>? <save_file_name>?
		The title and save_file_name arguments are optional. The title defaults to Worker Info and the plot is not saved on default.

	Extra arguments:
		'-a' - 'display all info from the transaction log'
		'-f' - 'flip colors between tasks'
		'-c' - 'display cache updates'
		'-r' - 'display resource updates'
		'-d' - 'display done markers'
		'-i' - 'display input transfers'
		'-o' - 'display output transfers'
		'-s' - 'print stats'
		'-x' - 'modify the sacle for the x ticks  -x <start> <step_size> <steps>'
		'-y' - 'modify the sacle for the y ticks  -y <start> <step_size> <steps>'
		'-m' - 'use manager start time as plot reference point Default: workers first task'


vine_plot_manager.py - produces a plot depicting the acummulation of events over time on the manager.

	Running the program: python vine_plot_manager.py <transaction_log> <title>? <save_file_name>?
		The title and save_file_name arguments are optional. The title defaults to Worker Info and the plot is not saved on default.


	Extra arguments:
		'-a' - 'display all info from the transaction log'
		'-c' - 'display connections'
		'-d' - 'display disconnections'
		'-r' - 'display resource updates'
		'-u' - 'display cache updates'
		'-s' - 'display sending tasks'
		'-w' - 'display notified results'
		'-m' - 'display marked done'
		'-i' - 'display input transfers'
		'-o' - 'display output transfes'

